1.1- Configuration Karma

- Configurer Karma


karma init karma.conf.js


- Editer le fichier karma.conf.js :

    basePath: 'www',
    
    files: [
        'lib/ionic/js/ionic.bundle.js',
        '../node_modules/angular-mocks/angular-mocks.js',
        
        'js/app.js',
        'js/**/*.module.js',
        'js/**/*.controller.js',
        'js/**/*.service.js',
        
        '../test/unit/**/*Spec.js',
    ],

